<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>New Contact Form Submission - Action Required</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>New Contact Form Submission - Action Required</h2>
  <p>
    Dear <%= name %>,<br><br>
    I hope this email finds you well. I wanted to inform you that we have received a new contact form submission on our website. The details of the submission are as follows:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></li>
    <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= phone %></li>
    <li><strong>Message:</strong> <%= message %></li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Please take the necessary steps to address this inquiry as soon as possible. The sender has shown interest in our <em>product/service/company</em>, and it is crucial that we provide a timely response to maintain excellent customer service.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can reach out to the individual using the provided email or phone number to address their concerns or answer any questions they may have. It is important to represent our company in a professional and helpful manner throughout the communication process.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you require any assistance or further information regarding this contact form submission, please feel free to contact me at <%= email %> or <%= phone %>.
  </p>
  <p>
    Thank you for your attention to this matter.
  </p>
  <p>
    Best regards,<br>
    <%= name %><br>
    
  </p>
</body>
</html>
